{"tid":2321122,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"建築工10月1日 管有打火機汽油等罪成候判 官指「好大可能判監」","createTime":"2020-12-11T09:41:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T17:09:42.000Z","uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ac0c1c189c7304d26a98ac7f1420ad2395079d2c","tid":2321122,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T09:41:31.000Z","msg":"24歲建築工人去年10月1日多區示威活動期間，在屯門警方封鎖線附近被截查，搜出打火機氣油、打火機及士巴拿，被控管有物品意圖損壞財產罪。裁判官梁雅忻今午於屯門裁判法院認為<span class=\"red\">被告被截查時身處位置距離非法活動現場不遠</span>，管有物品明顯能用以損壞財產，用以燃燒物品或拆除鐵欄，故裁定被告罪名成立。梁官押後判刑至<span class=\"red\">12月28日</span>下午，以待索取勞教中心報告，惟明言「好大可能判監」。<br />\n<br />\n被告馬**被控於去年10月1日在屯門杯渡路管有一樽355毫升打火機氣油、2個打火機及2個士巴拿，意圖在沒有合法辯解下使用該物品，以損毀他人財物。"},{"pid":"c68f02334d80a8c47bbfa1532b2c409ef5c14a12","tid":2321122,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T09:41:40.000Z","msg":"汁: 頭條"},{"pid":"034a2466adb73928e13ffbf7d1087c134446f510","tid":2321122,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T09:41:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b96e60ed3cc89d20d8911e8bf44148a46f83c058","tid":2321122,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T09:42:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53ec2267a5d905d080a2bc54e14693e907129bab","tid":2321122,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T09:43:47.000Z","msg":"方仲賢個日，無集會示威，無入電，咪又係告，仲要告到上區院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f77dc9e1b9bc02dfe33c729adfd5b6ed4f7b088c","tid":2321122,"uid":56115,"lik